                  <additions>
                     <p>Occasionally, Jones highlights sections of poetry that he particularly likes using curly brackets and stars. On fir, he has written "در سفر کر هفد بینی ورختن *** از دل تو/من کی رود حب الوطن" which is a slightly altered line from the Mas̱navī.</p>
